<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-452-002  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 452 002.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>DEC Professional  July 1989 v8 n7 p72(3).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>DEC Pro on line. (Text retrieval system on ARIS/BB accesses backissues of DEC Professional)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Schoeniger, Eric.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Subscribers to DEC Professional magazine will, after Aug 1989, beable to retrieve articles from back issues on-line.andP;  Thetext-retrieval system on the Automated Reader Information Servicebulletin board (ARIS/BB) will be able to access 10 years of DECProfessional and eventually all Professional Press publicationsfor free.andP;  To begin a keyword search a subscriber logs on toARIS/BB with the subscription number from the magazine's mailinglabel and chooses the text-retrieval option from the main menu.andO;The names of articles which contain the keyword entered by theuser are listed on the File screen, and from there they can beaccessed with arrow keys.andP;  There is also an on-line help featureavailable.andP;  The text-retrieval system is a customized version ofCC Software Inc's CC Search.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Topic:     DEC Professional (Periodical)Information ServicesComputer Bulletin BoardsSearchingTutorial.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>